The company should use a hybrid cloud for cloudifying since it's a mix of on-premises, 
private cloud and third-party, public cloud services.
Banking data should be kept on premise only since it's not secure over the cloud.
Healthcare, transport data can be stored over public or private cloud.

Since the company is growing and have a revenue of 18%, it's better if the company moves the infrastructure to cloud,
reducing the costs, virtualizing and giving more computing power.
The company can use Microsoft Azure, AWS cloud for the IaaS, SaaS, PaaS.
